cl-bls-signatures
=================

This library was extracted from the CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property
Chain) project.

Original Source: https://github.com/[username]/clpic
Source Module: src/crypto/bls/

The BLS signature implementation follows:
- IETF draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature-05 (BLS Signatures)
- IETF draft-irtf-cfrg-hash-to-curve-16 (Hash to Curve)
- Ethereum 2.0 BLS specification

This is a standalone extraction with no external dependencies.
All cryptographic primitives (SHA-256, HMAC-SHA256) are implemented
natively in Common Lisp.

Note: This implementation uses simulated curve operations for demonstration
purposes. For production use with real cryptographic security guarantees,
the curve arithmetic should be replaced with proper BLS12-381 field and
group operations.
